46
00:05:07,917 --> 00:05:09,241
Dari perkiraanku,...

47
00:05:09,243 --> 00:05:11,111
...kita akan bertarung
sampai malam lagi.

48
00:05:11,272 --> 00:05:15,100
- Kita tak bisa desak mereka lagi.
- Aku punya mata.

49
00:05:15,261 --> 00:05:17,900
Maaf. Aku cuma lelah.

50
00:05:18,061 --> 00:05:20,678
Kita semua lelah.

51
00:05:28,779 --> 00:05:31,354
Waspada.

52
00:05:45,629 --> 00:05:48,455
Ke perbatasan Utara.
Sekarang.

53
00:05:48,616 --> 00:05:51,000
- Hentikan para zombimu.
- Bukan punya kami.

54
00:05:51,161 --> 00:05:52,211
Benar.

55
00:05:52,372 --> 00:05:55,400
Bukan punya kami.

56
00:05:56,566 --> 00:05:58,625
Pergi ke perbatasan,
jangan bawa senjata,...

57
00:05:58,626 --> 00:05:59,755
...dan menunggu.

58
00:05:59,916 --> 00:06:01,068
Menunggu apa?

59
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:04,054
Dia.

60
00:06:14,083 --> 00:06:15,416
Tenang!

61
00:06:17,086 --> 00:06:19,511
Ini para zombi Ibumu?

62
00:06:19,672 --> 00:06:21,480
Bukan.

63
00:06:21,677 --> 00:06:23,511
Kurasa bukan.

64
00:06:23,672 --> 00:06:28,078
- Kenapa dia ingin bicara?
- Kalian memasuki wilayahnya.

65
00:06:28,219 --> 00:06:30,580
Sekali lagi.
Kalian harus jelaskan itu.

66
00:06:30,741 --> 00:06:33,775
Kita tak perlu ke sana.

67
00:06:33,936 --> 00:06:36,378
- Itu ide buruk.
- Kita sudah diserang.

68
00:06:36,539 --> 00:06:37,337
- Ya!
- Ya!

69
00:06:37,498 --> 00:06:39,089
Ini bukan para zombinya.

70
00:06:40,501 --> 00:06:43,100
Jika dia ingin kalian mati,
sudah dia utus gerombolan.

71
00:06:43,261 --> 00:06:45,020
Seluruhnya.
Bukan gelombang satu per satu.

72
00:06:45,181 --> 00:06:47,013
Mungkin
dia ingin kita lelah dahulu.

73
00:06:47,174 --> 00:06:49,618
Sudah saya sampaikan
di awal pertemuan ini,...

74
00:06:49,619 --> 00:06:52,100
...ada alasan untuk memercayai
bahwa satelit dan kebakaran...

75
00:06:52,261 --> 00:06:55,538
Aku tak mau dengar
satelit itu lagi, Eugene!

76
00:06:56,942 --> 00:06:59,018
Teman-temanku mati
demi selamatkan kalian...

77
00:06:59,019 --> 00:07:01,203
...dan kepala mereka berakhir
di atas tombak.

78
00:07:02,706 --> 00:07:04,623
Highwaymen ingin keadilan!

79
00:07:04,784 --> 00:07:06,002
- Ya!
- Ya!

80
00:07:06,168 --> 00:07:09,219
Jadi aku ingin kalian
mengajak kami...

81
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:11,287
...bertemu orang-orang aneh ini
di perbatasan...

82
00:07:11,289 --> 00:07:13,699
...dan kita penggal jalang itu!

83
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:15,058
Kita penggal!

84
00:07:15,219 --> 00:07:17,460
Lalu taruh kepala mereka
di atas tombak!

85
00:07:18,305 --> 00:07:20,700
- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Ya.

86
00:07:20,861 --> 00:07:23,257
Aku ingin cari udara segar.

87
00:07:31,902 --> 00:07:35,537
Kau lihat berapa zombi
di gerombolan Alpha?

88
00:07:36,715 --> 00:07:39,074
Puluhan ribu.

89
00:07:40,485 --> 00:07:41,510
Jadi...

90
00:07:41,671 --> 00:07:44,296
Apa rencanamu menghabisi mereka?

91
00:07:47,659 --> 00:07:49,500
Itu pertanyaan.

92
00:07:49,661 --> 00:07:51,679
Aku belum punya rencana.

93
00:07:53,165 --> 00:07:55,724
Yang lain ada?

94
00:07:57,335 --> 00:08:01,411
Jika dia kirim gerombolan itu,
tamat sudah!

95
00:08:01,572 --> 00:08:04,599
Saat ini,
dia cuma ingin bicara.

96
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,600
Dan kami akan dengarkan.

97
00:08:06,761 --> 00:08:10,699
Selagi kami bicara dengannya,
semua tetap fokus...

98
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:13,775
...untuk ancaman
dari Utara dan Selatan.

99
00:08:16,597 --> 00:08:18,900
Kita semua lelah.

100
00:08:20,061 --> 00:08:21,791
Kita di ujung jurang.

101
00:08:21,952 --> 00:08:25,400
Dan ini akan memburuk
sebelum membaik.

102
00:08:25,606 --> 00:08:32,627
Tetapi, kita tak akan melaluinya,
jika kita tak bersatu.

103
00:08:33,931 --> 00:08:35,700
Tiga arah ancaman
artinya tiga kelompok.

104
00:08:35,861 --> 00:08:37,381
Gabriel tetap di sini...

105
00:08:37,382 --> 00:08:40,000
...menjaga gerbang
dari gelombang Utara.

106
00:08:40,161 --> 00:08:42,045
Sementara Aaron mengajak
beberapa pasukan...

107
00:08:42,047 --> 00:08:45,989
...menangani gelombang Selatan,
sebelum mencapai pagar.

108
00:08:46,902 --> 00:08:49,600
Itu menyisakan kita,
dan perbatasannya.

109
00:08:49,761 --> 00:08:52,381
- Tanpa senjata.
- Kau benar mau pergi tanpa senjata?

110
00:08:52,542 --> 00:08:54,224
Tak ada pilihan lain.

111
00:09:08,758 --> 00:09:11,700
- Kami sudah pas.
- Kau kekurangan pasukan.

112
00:09:11,861 --> 00:09:14,900
Mereka juga kelelahan.
Ada Negan yang masih bugar.

113
00:09:15,061 --> 00:09:16,422
Kami sudah pas.

114
00:09:16,583 --> 00:09:20,184
Gabe. Boleh bicara?

115
00:09:22,821 --> 00:09:24,087
Dengar, Kawan,
sudah kubilang berulang kali....

116
00:09:24,089 --> 00:09:25,998
...aku lebih baik di sini
memanen tomat...

117
00:09:25,999 --> 00:09:27,055
...dan mengubur mayat.

118
00:09:27,216 --> 00:09:28,711
Dia membutuhkanmu di luar sana.

119
00:09:28,872 --> 00:09:30,353
Ya, aku ingin di sini,...

120
00:09:30,354 --> 00:09:32,000
...terutama di hari seperti ini.

121
00:09:32,161 --> 00:09:34,006
Lihatlah sekeliling,
semua orang kepanasan,...

122
00:09:34,008 --> 00:09:36,711
...marah pada kelompok kulit,
saling mengoceh sesama.

123
00:09:36,872 --> 00:09:38,194
Sudah kubilang, aku tak mau...

124
00:09:38,195 --> 00:09:40,400
...suasana kebencian itu
dilampiaskan padaku.

125
00:09:40,561 --> 00:09:42,989
Ini Aaron.
Dia orang baik.

126
00:09:43,851 --> 00:09:48,600
Aku cuma ingin tetap di sini.
Bisa bantu aku, Gabe?

127
00:09:48,761 --> 00:09:49,820
Kau bisa bertarung.

128
00:09:49,981 --> 00:09:52,024
Kau kekurangan petarung.

129
00:09:52,185 --> 00:09:54,123
Selai kacang, bertemu jelly.

130
00:09:54,284 --> 00:09:56,386
Kau ajak dia. Titik.

131
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:01,816
Jadi...

132
00:10:01,977 --> 00:10:03,800
Itu luar biasa.

133
00:10:03,961 --> 00:10:08,063
Cocok untukmu,
memakai pengganti tangan kuno.

134
00:10:44,019 --> 00:10:46,744
Lihat ini.

135
00:10:46,905 --> 00:10:48,930
Ya, ampun.

136
00:10:49,322 --> 00:10:52,024
Letakkan itu.

137
00:10:52,570 --> 00:10:54,200
Yang benar saja.

138
00:10:54,361 --> 00:10:56,512
Aku yakin Tuhan menaruh ini
karena suatu alasam...

139
00:10:56,514 --> 00:10:57,733
...untuk menolongku,
dan menolongmu...

140
00:10:57,894 --> 00:10:59,677
Taruh itu.

141
00:10:59,838 --> 00:11:03,119
Kita berdua tahu
sapu itu tak bisa menyayat.

142
00:11:09,044 --> 00:11:11,937
Aku mencoba
memperbaiki keadaan,...

143
00:11:11,939 --> 00:11:13,600
...dan aku bukan lagi pria
yang kau pikir...

144
00:11:13,761 --> 00:11:15,366
Ada tiga yang datang.

145
00:11:17,294 --> 00:11:20,001
Mereka di pihakmu.

146
00:11:20,297 --> 00:11:22,500
Benar. Baiklah.

147
00:11:22,661 --> 00:11:25,300
Aku tangani, Bos.

148
00:12:24,161 --> 00:12:26,628
Kau baik-baik saja?

149
00:12:27,864 --> 00:12:31,124
Aku ingin sendiri.

150
00:12:55,392 --> 00:12:58,401
Terima kasih telah membantuku.

151
00:12:58,636 --> 00:13:00,988
Aku bisa semalaman.

152
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:05,641
Kau ingin balik, 'kan?

153
00:13:07,979 --> 00:13:10,071
Aku tak apa-apa.

154
00:13:14,561 --> 00:13:16,895
Siaga.

155
00:13:53,858 --> 00:13:57,477
Ada satu peraturan
di antara kaum kita.

156
00:13:57,638 --> 00:13:59,700
Satu hukum.

157
00:13:59,861 --> 00:14:02,811
Tetap di tempat kalian.

158
00:14:02,972 --> 00:14:05,701
Namun, kalian tak patuh.

159
00:14:05,861 --> 00:14:09,011
Api bisa menghanguskan wilayahmu.

160
00:14:10,225 --> 00:14:12,620
Api sifatnya membakar.

161
00:14:12,781 --> 00:14:15,133
Kami tak punya masalah
dengan alam.

162
00:14:15,294 --> 00:14:17,744
Itu bisa menghanguskan
salah satu komunitas kami.

163
00:14:17,905 --> 00:14:20,700
Kami tak bisa duduk diam
dan biarkan itu terjadi.

164
00:14:20,861 --> 00:14:21,911
Kau bisa maklumi itu.

165
00:14:22,072 --> 00:14:24,711
Kami cuma melintasi sekali.

166
00:14:24,872 --> 00:14:26,981
Tiga kali.

167
00:14:29,227 --> 00:14:32,903
Saat kebakaran,
kalian memasuki wilayahku.

168
00:14:33,064 --> 00:14:36,691
Saat badai musim dingin,
kalian memasuki wilayahku.

169
00:14:36,852 --> 00:14:40,069
Saat pencarian di sungai,...

170
00:14:40,071 --> 00:14:43,214
...kau dan pria bertangan besi
memasuki wilayahku.

171
00:14:43,375 --> 00:14:46,100
Itu tiga kali.

172
00:14:46,261 --> 00:14:51,581
Kami selalu mengawasi.

173
00:14:55,512 --> 00:14:59,272
Ingat perkataanku
soal melintasi perbatasanku?

174
00:15:05,005 --> 00:15:07,522
Kalian harus dihukum.

175
00:15:17,684 --> 00:15:19,775
Tetapi...

176
00:15:19,776 --> 00:15:23,180
...aku lebih memilih berbincang.

177
00:15:23,341 --> 00:15:26,111
Tak ada pertumpahan darah kali ini.

178
00:15:26,272 --> 00:15:27,783
Jadi apa maumu?

179
00:15:29,546 --> 00:15:31,795
Tanah.

180
00:15:31,956 --> 00:15:34,048
Sungai yang berembus
sampai ke lembah,...

181
00:15:34,050 --> 00:15:35,970
...itu perbatasan Selatan baru kalian.

182
00:15:36,131 --> 00:15:38,700
Kami nanti menandai
perbatasan Utara baru.

183
00:15:38,861 --> 00:15:40,211
Itu memotong
wilayah perburuan kami.

184
00:15:40,372 --> 00:15:42,207
Kita tak perlu berdiri di sini
dan mendengar si...

185
00:15:42,368 --> 00:15:44,221
Carol!

186
00:15:44,382 --> 00:15:47,803
"Si"...

187
00:15:47,805 --> 00:15:49,990
...apa?

188
00:15:52,219 --> 00:15:55,000
- Si omong kosong ini.
- Cukup.

189
00:15:55,161 --> 00:15:56,170
Ayo. Kita selesai.

190
00:15:56,331 --> 00:15:58,647
- Ayo pergi.
- Belum.

191
00:16:01,819 --> 00:16:06,080
Sampai satu ini
menundukkan kepalanya.

192
00:16:16,076 --> 00:16:20,800
- Kau harus takut padaku.
- Aku tak takut.

193
00:16:20,961 --> 00:16:25,432
Aku melihatmu
dan tak merasa apa-apa.

194
00:16:26,436 --> 00:16:28,820
Benar begitu?

195
00:16:30,257 --> 00:16:32,848
Bocah pirang itu...

196
00:16:32,850 --> 00:16:37,095
...meneriaki namamu
sesaat sebelum dia dipenggal.

197
00:16:43,770 --> 00:16:46,723
Hentikan!

198
00:16:46,884 --> 00:16:51,311
Aku minta maaf atas temanku.

199
00:16:51,472 --> 00:16:53,213
Kami belum tidur.

200
00:16:53,374 --> 00:16:56,330
Dan kau tahu dia kehilangan siapa.

201
00:16:59,434 --> 00:17:01,219
Aku memaafkanmu.

202
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:04,455
Sebagai sesama Ibu.

203
00:17:07,736 --> 00:17:12,647
Ini wilayahku sekarang.
Kalian sebaiknya lari.

204
00:17:12,808 --> 00:17:14,374
Cepat, ayo pergi.

205
00:17:15,986 --> 00:17:18,137
Ayo pergi.

206
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:43,927
Dengar.

207
00:17:44,088 --> 00:17:47,023
- Aku tahu kau menghadapi...
- Jalang itu harus mati.

208
00:17:58,787 --> 00:18:01,522
Dia berbeda sejak pergi
dari kapal itu.

209
00:18:01,683 --> 00:18:06,518
Dia mending naik kapal saja.
Menemukan kedamaian.

210
00:18:06,689 --> 00:18:09,862
Dia harus bersama kita.

211
00:18:10,023 --> 00:18:11,500
Dia pun tak tidur.

212
00:18:11,661 --> 00:18:14,633
Dia terjaga semalaman
mencari mereka.

213
00:18:27,482 --> 00:18:29,048
Sial.

214
00:18:29,209 --> 00:18:32,134
- Ada apa?
- Para Whisperer.

215
00:18:32,295 --> 00:18:34,233
- Ada tiga orang.
- Nyalakan walkie.

216
00:18:34,394 --> 00:18:37,000
Berpencar... Utara, Barat.
Kami di Timur.

217
00:18:37,161 --> 00:18:38,900
Tangkap! Jangan bunuh!

218
00:18:57,495 --> 00:18:59,412
Hei, kau...

219
00:18:59,573 --> 00:19:01,089
Ingat kataku?

220
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,000
Aku terpaksa.

221
00:19:04,161 --> 00:19:06,853
Kau tak melihat...

222
00:19:09,858 --> 00:19:11,511
Kau ingin aku gantung diri?

223
00:19:11,672 --> 00:19:12,934
Ikat tanganmu.
Kubawa kau pulang.

224
00:19:13,095 --> 00:19:14,276
Membawaku pulang?

225
00:19:14,437 --> 00:19:16,529
Itu berita terbaik
yang kudengar hari ini!

226
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:20,091
Tapi aku tak mau terikat
seperti tahanan perang.

227
00:19:20,252 --> 00:19:22,343
Ya, akan begitu.

228
00:19:22,704 --> 00:19:25,296
Atau apa, Jagoan?

229
00:19:32,121 --> 00:19:35,205
Kau tahu yang kulihat?

230
00:19:35,366 --> 00:19:39,344
Kulihat seseorang
yang sedang pura-pura.

231
00:19:40,722 --> 00:19:42,764
Ayo pergi, Kawan.

232
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:47,511
Tuhan.

233
00:19:47,672 --> 00:19:50,022
Kau menyandungku?

234
00:19:50,183 --> 00:19:52,232
Apa kau bocah 12 tahun?

235
00:19:52,393 --> 00:19:54,467
Ada apa denganmu?

236
00:19:54,628 --> 00:19:56,979
Aku sudah ambil resiko
demi kalian...

237
00:19:56,980 --> 00:19:58,200
...selama seharian!

238
