00:43:24,142 --> 00:43:26,900
Kita butuh selai.

485
00:43:27,061 --> 00:43:29,972
Mungkin ada di toko.
Tunggu sebentar.

486
00:43:31,819 --> 00:43:34,237
- Itu dia.
- Terima kasih.

487
00:43:36,731 --> 00:43:40,307
Kau yakin toko sudah buka?

488
00:43:41,311 --> 00:43:42,577
Ibu?

489
00:43:44,056 --> 00:43:46,211
Mau ke mana?

490
00:44:15,863 --> 00:44:17,821
Bagaimana lukanya?

491
00:44:20,275 --> 00:44:23,076
Sakit.

492
00:44:24,446 --> 00:44:26,187
Kembali di sini juga menyakitkan.

493
00:44:26,348 --> 00:44:29,000
Dan itu salah Alpha.
