494
00:44:29,161 --> 00:44:33,103
Kita cuma bertujuh.
Aku harus pikirkan mereka.

495
00:44:33,264 --> 00:44:34,296
Aku tahu.

496
00:44:35,941 --> 00:44:38,675
Tapi aku sungguh melihat mereka.

497
00:44:41,947 --> 00:44:44,431
Hanya kau saja.

498
00:44:54,476 --> 00:44:56,976
Sudah aman?

499
00:44:58,447 --> 00:45:01,297
Untuk saat ini.

500
00:45:33,348 --> 00:45:36,348
Merah muda cocok untukmu.

501
00:45:41,523 --> 00:45:44,307
Michonne tak percayai aku.

502
00:45:52,774 --> 00:45:54,751
Kalau kau?

503
00:45:58,373 --> 00:46:00,924
Ya.

